{"tid":217225,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警員反爆竊行動期間 遭盜竊背包","createTime":"2017-04-25T15:42:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T04:56:05.000Z","uid":5195,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"de4aa48157f139d0697a68ba25e407bd1f6898e2","tid":217225,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:42:42.000Z","msg":"今日凌晨2時許，一名隸屬香港仔分區特遣隊的警員，在香港仔漁光道進行反爆竊行動期間，遺下其背包，內有一支伸縮警棍、一支胡椒噴劑、一部警察通訊器及其個人物品，人員其後未能尋回該背包。<br />\n<br />\n西區警區重案組接手調查，其後在石排灣邨，<strong>以涉嫌盜竊</strong>拘捕一名姓陳(59歲)本地男子，並起回該背包及部分物品，惟該伸縮警棍及胡椒噴劑仍未被尋回。<br />\n<br />\n警方呼籲市民如拾獲有關物品，應立即致電999，並將該等物品交到就近的警署，或致電<br />\n3660 1300<br />\n與香港仔警署人員聯絡。<br />\n<br />\n警方重申，就裝備的保管及使用有嚴格的規定，警方會就有關事件展開內部調查，如發現有人員違規，定會嚴肅處理。"},{"pid":"f545ad32cac0cd07a590ec66a65cbff796255dc3","tid":217225,"uid":51933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:43:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1cd12aff309c7e6e139279cf8d9323968b23b7c5","tid":217225,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:45:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />黑警"},{"pid":"75861dd83d01427b41a4c09f16497ff819dcbe88","tid":217225,"uid":42188,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:46:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">呀sir俾人偷野唔洗你教</span></span>"},{"pid":"987662a04718daa94c1ffaac253bc030445ead9c","tid":217225,"uid":20965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:46:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14c9daaff4e5711ccb8be2c0a6b159584cda70cd","tid":217225,"uid":3581,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-25T15:47:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\